import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../../components/navbar'
import {Segment, Container, Image, Divider, Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react'

const About = () => {
    return(
        <>
            <Navbar/>
            <Segment vertical>
                <Container text>
                    <Image src='secondBangkok.png' size='medium' circular />
                    <Divider as={"h4"} horizontal>
                        <Icon name={"map marker alternate"}/>
                        Chicago
                    </Divider>
                    Yoooo about meeeee
                    More about me
                </Container>
            </Segment>
        </>
    )
}

export default About
